data.title: Minnesota Cities by Population (2024)
data.meta_description: Get a list of Minnesota cities by population based on Census 2023 data.
data.text:
The most populated cities in Minnesota are Minneapolis with 425,115, St. Paul at 303,820, Rochester with 122,413, Duluth at 87,680, and Bloomington with 87,398. You can get the most current Census population data for all 913 Minnesota cities, sorted from the most populous cities in Minnesota to the least, according to the 2023 Population Estimates Program and 2022 American Community Survey.
